title: Yoh! Emtee calls Cassper and AKA 'losers'
text:
He seemed to have the upper hand until he replied to one tweep saying, "If you want a loser to play with follow Casper or AKA b*tch". 


Tweeps continued to question his recent upgrades in the form of a big house and new car. He maintained that he worked hard for all he has and looked carefully at his contract, unlike his ex-stable mates. 
But Cassper and AKA stans (steady fans) could not get over the indirect diss. Why implicate AKA and Cassper in a twar that does not involve them?
